Description: Rim sherd of Chian Wild Goat Style pottery dinos; white slip; interior reserved save for black band at rim; exterior: on flat rim, guilloche; below on body, traces of diagonal strokes.
Bibliographic references: Lemos 1991 / Archaic Pottery of Chios. The Decorated Styles (p. 246, no. 286)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GD.0010) (phase 2)
